The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | I needed a change: Ishant
                                                                                                                                                                                                     I needed a change: Ishant
            A CORRESPONDENT                      
	Bangalore: Ishant Sharma felt it was time for a change and so decided to have a hair cut.         
	I felt like I needed a change So decided to have a hair cut, Ishant said on Sunday.         
	My teammates were also ragging me and asking me to go to the barber         
	If my teammates are happy, it also makes me feel the same, he added.                                                                                                                          
